FBIS4-63105 "drsov098__a94006" FBIS-SOV-94-098-A Daily Report 20 May 1994 ANNEX Russia International Affairs Polish Embassy in Moscow Evacuated After Bomb Threat Polish Embassy in Moscow Evacuated After Bomb Threat LD1305153694 Warsaw PAP in English 1533 GMT 13 May 94--FOR OFFICIAL USE ONLY LD1305153694 Warsaw PAP English BFN [Text] Moscow, May 13 -- All staff from the Polish Embassy in Moscow was evacuated on Friday afternoon after the embassy received a bomb warning through telephone. The building is being checked jointly by Polish Embassy security personnel and Russian bomb experts.
